7460|title=Filmregisseur Dusan Makavejev gestorben|date=January 25, 2019|website=Berliner Zeitung}}</ref>\n** [[Krishna Sobti]], Indian Hindi-language fiction writer and essayist (b. [[1925]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiapost.com/hindi-author-krishna-sobti-dies-at-93/|title=Hindi author Krishna Sobti dies at 93}}</ref>\n* [[January 26]]\n** [[Jean Guillou]], French composer, organist, and pianist (b. [[1930]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.resmusica.com/2019/01/27/disparition-de-jean-guillou/|title=D\u00e9c\u00e8s de Jean Guillou \u00ab Flash Info \u00ab ResMusica|first=La|last=R\u00e9daction}}</ref>\n** [[Michel Legrand]], French composer (b. [[1932]])<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.france24.com/en/20190126-oscar-winning-french-composer-michel-legrand-dies-86|title=Oscar-winning French composer Michel Legrand dies at 86|date=January 26, 2019|website=France 24}}</ref>\n* [[January 27]] \u2013 [[Nina Fyodorova]], Russian cross-country skier (b. [[1947]])<ref>[https://78.ru/news/2019-01-28/v_peterburge_skonchalas_olimpiiskaya_chempionka_nina_baldicheva \u0412 \u041f\u0435\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0431\u0443\u0440\u0433\u0435 \u0441\u043a\u043e\u043d\u0447\u0430\u043b\u0430\u0441\u044c \u043e\u043b\u0438\u043c\u043f\u0438\u0439\u0441\u043a\u0430\u044f \u0447\u0435\u043c\u043f\u0438\u043e\u043d\u043a\u0430 \u041d\u0438\u043d\u0430 \u0411\u0430\u043b\u0434\u044b\u0447\u0435\u0432\u0430] {{in lang|ru}}</ref>\n* [[January 29]] \u2013 [[James Ingram]], American R&B musician (b. [[1952]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/james-ingram-dead-grammy-winning-r-b-singer-was-66-1180817|title=James Ingram, Grammy-Winning R&B Singer, Dies at 66|website=The Hollywood Reporter}}</ref>\n* [[January 30]] \u2013 [[Dick Miller]], American actor (b. [[1928]])<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://variety.com/2019/film/obituaries-people-news/dick-miller-dead-dies-gremlins-terminator-1203124265/|title=Dick Miller, 'Gremlins' and 'Terminator' Actor, Dies at 90|first1=Nate|last